{"type": "article", "id": 12343, "title": "为了体现电力持久，金霸王把hello kitty变成了骷髅", "description": "吓死宝宝了。", "date": "2015-07-20T13:33:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 143, "name": "设计"}, {"id": 13164, "name": "金霸王"}, {"id": 5557, "name": "DDB"}, {"id": 13165, "name": "Grey"}, {"id": 329, "name": "宝洁"}, {"id": 13166, "name": "伯克希尔哈撒韦"}, {"id": 2394, "name": "巴菲特"}], "category": 18, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604230705VrMqDXzO3cnPCNdm.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>小朋友们，你们可以一直玩电动玩具，直到它们都变成不死不休的骷髅……当然这都多亏了我们（电力持久的金霸王）。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230703Lnbgs8XeqYpZrkyi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.484375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n<span></span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这是金霸王近日推出的一组广告，用瘆人的骷髅玩具形象展示他们的电力有多么持久，要多持久有多持久，哪怕久到你开始有点害怕。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230703GcVrCx7OUmTYsJRl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n<span></span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这组广告由全球第七大广告公司</span><span> Grey </span><span>伦敦办事处策划，看起来这次推出的 “</span><span>Toys Should  Live Forever</span><span>”</span><span> (</span><span>玩具应该长生不老</span><span>)</span><span>标语创意脱胎自 </span><span>2013 </span><span>年的 “</span><span>Some Toys\r\nNever Die</span><span>” </span><span>(</span><span>有些玩具永远不死</span><span>)</span><span>标语，不过当时这组获奖作品是由 </span><span>Grey </span><span>新加坡操刀设计。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230704uxcnAOUgv9sNZIlX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.728125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>害怕“被自己扔掉的玩具报复”，是很多小孩子童年的噩梦吧。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><span>DDB</span><span> 米兰曾经为德国汉高旗下品牌乐泰瞬干胶制作一组类似的广告，选择的则是被粘合好的玩具回到小主人怀抱的温馨主题。</span><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230704vcD4LlUetC7NnMfj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><em>Advertising Agency: DDB Milan, Italy</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><span style=\"text-align:start;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">创立于 1920 年的消费品品牌金霸王，在经历了 1996 年与吉列公司合并，2005 年随着吉列被宝洁以 570 亿美元收购后，在去年成为了宝洁品牌“瘦身”计划的第一批清理对象，<span style=\"text-align:start;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">被巴菲特麾下的伯克希尔哈撒韦公司( Berkshire Hathaway )</span>斥资 47 亿美元收购，这笔交易还将为金霸王资产重组注资 18 亿美元现金。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><span style=\"text-align:start;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">市场认为巴菲特此举是出于看好消费电池市场，金霸王电池在该领域已开发出智能手机电池、应急电源甚至云储等产品，并且可以动用手中价值不菲的宝洁公司股票，<span><span style=\"text-align:start;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">伯克希尔公司</span></span>目前是宝洁的第五大股东。</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}